      "date": "2016-10-20 04:40:29.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1: Verified+1\n\nTests uploaded by Trevis Autotest2 from trevis-42vm1 for review-dne-part-1 received by maloo, run on CentOS Linux 7/x86_64: (https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sessions/15d118b2-967f-11e6-9722-5254006e85c2). Ran 7 tests. No failures.",
